      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## BHP AAP Report vs Live BI Connector API\nCompares BHP\u2019s 10-month production figures (July 2025 \u2013 April 2026, 434,668 jobs) against what the BI connector REST API currently returns from the demo system.\n\n**Two types of gaps identified:**\n- \ud83d\udd34 **API Coverage Gap** \u2014 this metric is not exposed by any BI connector endpoint\n- \ud83d\udfe1 **Data Volume Gap** \u2014 the API CAN provide this, but the demo system has less data than BHP\u2019s production fleet",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
