      "gridPos": {
        "h": 16,
        "w": 14,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 34
      },
      "id": 17,
      "options": {
        "content": "The following BHP report metrics have **no equivalent endpoint** in the current BI connector API. These represent feature gaps that would need to be addressed to fully replicate this report from the API alone.\n\n| BHP Metric | BHP Value | API Available? | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Total Compute Hours | 22,032 hrs | \u274c Not exposed | Task duration data not in any endpoint |\n| Person-Work-Days | 2,754 days | \u274c Not exposed | Derived from compute hours |\n| Person-Years | 11.5 years | \u274c Not exposed | Derived metric |\n| Unique Job Templates | 466 | \u274c No templates endpoint | No `/api/v1/bi/templates/` exists |\n| Inventory Scope | 8,069 hosts | \u274c Not exposed | Inventory data not in stored models |\n| Organizations | 11 | \u274c Not directly countable | Org IDs in job summaries but no org list |\n| Avg Tasks/Run | 18,777\u201368,809 | \u274c Not exposed | Task-level granularity not in API |\n| Domain Classification | 6 domains | \u274c Not exposed | Module-level data not in stored models |\n| Module-level stats | win_shell, uri, etc. | \u274c Not exposed | No module breakdown endpoint |",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "API Coverage Gaps",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 16,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 14,
        "y": 34
      },
      "id": 18,
      "options": {
        "content": "The BI connector API successfully provides:\n\n\u2705 **Host automation data** \u2014 `StoredHostMetric`\n- Hostname, first/last automation, automation counter\n- Active vs deleted host tracking\n\n\u2705 **Job-host relationships** \u2014 `StoredJobHostSummary`\n- Which hosts ran which jobs\n- Organisation and inventory context\n\n\u2705 **Daily aggregated metrics** \u2014 `DailyMetricsSummary`\n- Job counts (total, successful, failed, canceled)\n- Event type breakdowns (ok, failed, skipped)\n- Credential counts by type\n\n\u2705 **Hourly collection log** \u2014 `HourlyMetricsCollection`\n- Per-collector-type hourly volume\n- 3,288 event collection records\n\n\u2705 **Collection pipeline** \u2014 `CollectionBatch`\n- Batch history, status, records imported\n- Collection timing and coverage windows",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "What the BI Connector DOES Provide",
      "type": "text"
    },
